==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Regius
<hw>Re"gi*us</hw> <pr>(r?l"?*?s)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>regius</ets>, from <ets>rex</ets>, <ets>regis</ets>, a king.]</ety>
<def>Of or pertaining to a king; royal.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Regius professor</b></col>, <cd>an incumbent of a
professorship founded by royal bounty, as in an English
university.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Regive</ent>⟦br⟧
